{"tid":2012758,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不一樣的母親節 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-05-12T01:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T01:06:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52688929b8c2eecfbf468ab97ca0dbc0805612fb","tid":2012758,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T01:06:10.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200512/20916282/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200512%2F20916282%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HXjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=4cbd7bf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200512%2F20916282%2F&h=fb409a53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200512/20916282/</a><br />\n<br />\n不一樣的母親節 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200512/large/1589179103_d51d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200512%2Flarge%2F1589179103_d51d.jpg&h=d2028b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛過去的星期天，香港人經歷了一個不一樣的母親節，有13歲的學生記者被警察濫捕，在鏡頭前抽泣着同媽媽說：「母親節快樂！對唔住&hellip;&hellip;」；有母親帶着兩個分別12歲及14歲的女兒外出宵夜慶祝母親節，離開餐廳時遇上警察行動，結果兩個女兒被捕，母親要隔着馬路聲淚俱下呼叫女兒：「唔駛驚，媽咪見到你哋了！」；有香港人選出來的代議士，被一群警察撻生魚似撻向地面，再被防暴警用膝蓋強壓頸肩部位，再被餵以胡椒噴霧；有女記者在現場採訪，被防暴警視作江洋大盜，用手箍頸20秒，女記者一度休克，需戴上頸箍送院；防暴警察進入旺角商場噴射胡椒噴霧，在食肆進餐的食客中招，痛苦莫名，其中包括年輕的母親及她胸前抱着的目測一兩歲大的幼女&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。，竟在網絡貼出一個橙色公文袋的相片。那是她收到的母親節禮物。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，這種人，有甚麼資格做母親？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"}]}